a39c0f6615699bfbed13411cc6990756ce0e25dcd9d21dfce83b130ab8d0adeeb1e7fca1577732b02c886da52eeddd121987f861418ad85f93907e5a47bfcf02  disable-test-missing-ckeygen.patch"
